		<center>
			<h2>Ryuichi Sakamoto and Toshio Iwai<br>
			on the Internet on Dec. 16th, 1996</h2>
		</center>
		<p>
		<hr noshade size="2">
		</p>
		<ul>
			<h3><img src="../../../images/blue-dot.gif">Outline and our challenges</h3>
			<p class="size2">YOU CAN WATCH THE MUSIC CONCERT ON THE INTERNET.<br>
			Ryuichi Sakamoto, the world's famous musician contributed to YMO and the main theme of the movie &quot;Last Emperor,&quot; and Toshio Iwai, an interactive media artist, will play great music with audiences on the Internet.<br>
			We have decided the experiment of broadcasting will be held on the schedule -- in the evening on 16th of December, 1996 (JST)<br>
			Through this experiment, we expect to show the power of video/audio broadcasting with commercial available software, and to examine how it works over the AI3 environment. The audio and video will be fed to Indonesia and Hong Kong from Japan. This event was designed as an official domestic event in Japan presented by <a href="http://park.org/">Internet 1996 World Expo</a>, however, we achieved to get it also for Asian countries. You may get more information about the concert from <a href="http://japan.park.org/Japan/1216/index-e.html">http://japan.park.org/Japan/1216/index-e.html</a></p>
			<p class="size2">The concert is held at Mito Tower Hall, north of Tokyo. It is aways from AI3-IX over 600km.<br>
			Enjoy!</p>
			<p><img src="map.gif"></p>
			<p>
			<hr noshade size="2">
			</p>
			<h3><img src="../../../images/blue-dot.gif">How to join the concert</h3>
			<p class="size2">To watch and listen to the broadcast, you may use a multimedia player such as <a href="http://www.xingtech.com/"><b>StreamWorks</b></a>.<br>
			You can get StreamWorks clients from Xing Technology Corp.<br>
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="size2"><a href="http://www.xingtech.com/sw_now.html">Download Page</a>
			</ul>
			<p class="size2">We provide several StreamWorks Network Server for the propagation of the concert. Below is the list of the addresses:<br>
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li type="disc" class="size2">Click here to <a href="over.html">Hibiya IWE Network Center (Tokyo)</a>
				<li type="disc" class="size2">Click here to <a href="over.html">Kyusyu Univ. (Fukuoka)</a>
			</ul>
			<p class="size2">Especially for AI3 partners, we also provide a exclusive server at AI3-IX (Nara) for a better quality of distribution. To join this concert from AI3 partners side, try following address:</p>
			<ul>
				<li type="disc" class="size2">Click here to <a href="over.html">AI3-IX (AI3 partner only)</a>
			</ul>
			<p class="size2">With a StreamWorks broadcasting we will also provide low bandwidth sound with <a href="http://www.realaudio.com/"><b>RealAudio</b></a>. We have only a RealAudio Server at the concert hall in Mito, Japan. Unfortunately we could not arrange RealAudio redistribution server only for AI3, so you may get worth quality with it. Anyway try this :-)</p>
			<ul>
				<li type="disc" class="size2"><a href="http://www.soum.co.jp/mito/">Mito Tower Hall</a>
			</ul>
			<p class="size2">You cat get RealAudio clients from Progressive Networks.</p>
			<ul>
